dct_title_s: Map of part of Bolivia from the surveys of J. B. Minchin, to illustrate the paper by G. C. Musters, retired Commander R.N.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes second panel with continuation of map, encompassing areas northwest including La Paz and Lake Titicaca. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 47, (1877), pp. 201-16; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.47 1877
dct_publisher_sm: London: published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by John Murray, Albemarle Street, 1877.
call_number_s: G5321.B5 1877 .R6 z Map is accompanied by a book.
